  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n\r\n*Summary*: \r\nThe keyboard doesn't appear at once when using send command for the second time\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe keyboard should appear when the user use Send command\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe keyboard doesn't appear at once when user uses Send command for the second time. So the user has to tap on the input field to get the keyboard.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Launch app \"Status\"\r\n- Login with valid credentials\r\n- Go to 1-1 chat\r\n- Tap on the Send command\r\n- Chhose the recepient and type the ammount\r\n- Send the ammount\r\n- Tap on the Send command again\r\n\r\nVideo:\r\nhttps://drive.google.com/open?id=0B0pYIvdvIoAHNnA0MDZjQWZ5T0E\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: 0.9.8-56-gd743691+\r\n* Operating System: Android 5.0\r\n\r\n",
