    "body": "The initial bug report contains video where popup with error is shown instead of successful send flow. The issue (no keyboard is shown if use /send or /request command second time) happens for the normal flow too and this is the main issue to be fixed. \r\n\r\nHere is a video (and log) with normal flow, start from 0:20 (1st send) and 00:43-00:46 (shows 2nd send with issue) https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/6448327/sessions/9/?accessToken=ADYnYmjPJvAMxtqOLmxdFoeyE/c\r\n\r\nSo, it's expected to get this state after choosing a recipient:\r\n![screenshot_20170828-193157](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/29784020-36332c9c-8c2b-11e7-83cb-3355d7ad8002.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nBut issue is that no keyboard is shown, so user needs to tap inside the input field to get to the expected state:\r\n\r\n![screenshot_20170828-193219](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/29784060-4fd481f0-8c2b-11e7-955b-344c93bb7822.png)\r\n",
